      "role": "user",
      "content": "well i'm not talking about just \"feelings\" or something psychological. it feels more like a literal vibration. if you look at the positioning of the belt stars, they are way too precise. wouldnt it be scientifically possible for a massive array to be positioned there to broadcast something? like a surveillance network that's been there long before we even had tech?",
